Numerical computation

We discretize Î£ with a regular grid and index the grid centers by xi,j = (ih1 +x0,0,1 , jh2 +x0,0,2 ).
The whole domain Î£ is approximated by cell fields with constant on each cell. For any field v,
vÌƒ denotes the vector of its values on the grid cells.

